<br>
I created a silent MP3 that gives warning beeps at 4:30 and 4:45.  It provides an excellent in-game, on screen timer and it autorepeats, so after you press play when the first one goes off there's nothing else to press.  I usually hit DA at about 4:52 on the MP3 player.<br>
<br>
The MP3 can be downloaded here: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.twistoffate.org/forums/viewtopic.php?t=74">www.twistoffate.org/forum...c.php?t=74</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
